          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're tired of juggling multiple tools for lead generation, outreach, and data management, Apollo.io is here to simplify your life. As a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "sales intelligence platform with AI",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", it's constantly evolving to meet the demands of modern B2B sales. I've been using it for months, and the recent updates have genuinely streamlined my workflow—think of it as having a smart assistant that handles the heavy lifting. Let me walk you through what's new and why it might be the upgrade your team needs. Ready to dive in? ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Check out Apollo.io's latest features here",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Discover Apollo.io's Latest Innovations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Apollo.io rolls out updates that feel less like incremental tweaks and more like leaps forward. Here are the standout new features that have caught my eye:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Assistant Enhancements",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The AI chat now offers deeper context for emails and research. For instance, I recently used it to generate a personalized follow-up sequence for a cold lead, and it pulled in relevant company news automatically—saving me 20 minutes per outreach. It’s like having a research intern who never sleeps.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Improved Data Enrichment",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": With a B2B database of over 275 million contacts, Apollo.io has always been a powerhouse, but the new enrichment algorithms are sharper. They now cross-reference more sources to ensure email deliverability, reducing bounce rates in my campaigns by nearly 15%.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automated Scoring Upgrades",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The lead scoring system now incorporates intent signals from web activity. I saw this in action when a prospect visited our pricing page multiple times; Apollo.io flagged them as high-intent, prompting a timely email that led to a demo booking. These features aren't just additions—they're practical tools that drive real results.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-apollo-io"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a deeper dive into how these updates work, explore ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
