      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is Apollo.io Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Apollo.io isn't just for large enterprises; it's versatile enough to fit various sales scenarios. Based on my experience and user feedback, here’s who will benefit most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Startup Sales Teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": If you're bootstrapping your pipeline, the free tier offers 900 credits monthly to test features like sequences and prospecting. I started with this when launching a new product, and it helped build my first 50 qualified leads without upfront costs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "B2B Marketers and SDRs",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": The automated email sequences and scoring make it perfect for high-volume outreach. One colleague reduced their manual data entry by 70% by syncing Apollo.io with their CRM.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enterprises Looking to Unify Tools",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Apollo.io acts as a single platform for outbound, inbound, and deal execution. Instead of paying for separate tools, you get everything from data enrichment to pipeline management—streamlining tech stacks as mentioned in their pricing tiers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
