        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Time-Saving Automation",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Sequences handle follow-ups, and AI research cuts down prep time. This freed up my schedule to focus on closing deals rather than administrative tasks.",
